## Find All books
GET http://localhost:8080/books
Accept: application/json

### Find All Books with min pages equals
GET http://localhost:8080/books/min-pages/500
Accept: application/json

### Find By Id
@id = 6a3559b6cb259680688b9d74
GET http://localhost:8080/books/findById/{{id}}
Accept: application/json


### Find By Id
@year = 2008
GET http://localhost:8080/books/findByYear/{{year}}
Accept: application/json

### Create Book
POST http://localhost:8080/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Ricas Code",
  "pages": 431,
  "year": 2008,
  "authors": [
    "Ricardo Mello",
    "Maria Silva"
  ]
}

### Update Book
@idUpdate = 6a3551be4105f41dede3ef97
PUT http://localhost:8080/books/{{idUpdate}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Ricas Code - Updated",
  "pages": 464,
  "year": 2008,
  "authors": [
    "", ""
  ]
}

### Delete Book
@idDelete = 6a3551be4105f41dede3ef97
DELETE http://localhost:8080/books/{{idDelete}}